# MacroPulse — Simple Working GitHub Deploy Version

This is the SIMPLEST stable architecture that will work directly on GitHub Pages.

No backend required.
No broken CORS proxies.
No fake data.

Uses:

* CoinGecko
* FinancialModelingPrep

Both work directly from browser.

---

# FILE STRUCTURE

Create ONLY ONE FILE:

```bash
index.html
```

Upload it to GitHub Pages.

